{
  "texts": [
    "Lectures were conducted face-to-face for two hours each, during which the instructor utilized PowerPoint presentations and a code editor to explain concepts and demonstrate their practical application though coding.",
    "Students were encouraged to bring their laptops to class for hands-on practice alongside the instructor.",
    "Ten lab assignments were given throughout the semester, each with a one-week deadline.",
    "Additionally, graded in-class practice activities were held on the 4th, 7th, and 12th weeks of the semester.",
    "During these activities, students were tasked with completing a programming exercise and submitting it by the end of the session."
  ]
}